182    /**
183     * Create a new {@code FattyAcidParserEventHandler}.
184     *
185     * @param knownFunctionalGroups the known functional groups
186     */

188        this.knownFunctionalGroups = knownFunctionalGroups;

200                    entry("cistrans_post_event", this::set_cistrans),
201                    entry("acid_type_double_post_event", this::check_db),
202                    entry("db_length_pre_event", this::open_db_length),
203                    entry("db_length_post_event", this::close_db_length),
204                    // lengths
205                    entry("functional_length_pre_event", this::reset_length),
206                    entry("fatty_length_pre_event", this::reset_length),
207                    entry("functional_length_post_event", this::set_functional_length),
208                    entry("fatty_length_post_event", this::set_fatty_length),
209                    // numbers
210                    entry("notation_specials_pre_event", this::special_number),

213                    // functional groups

279    private String FA_I() {
280        return "fa" + Integer.toString(fattyAcylStack.size());
281    }
282
283    private void set_lipid_level(LipidLevel _level) {
284        level = level.level < _level.level ? level : _level;
285    }
286
287    @Override
288    protected void resetParser(TreeNode node) {
289        content = null;
290        level = LipidLevel.FULL_STRUCTURE;
291        headgroup = "";
292        fattyAcylStack = new ArrayDeque<>();
293        fattyAcylStack.add(new FattyAcid("FA", knownFunctionalGroups));
294        tmp = new Dictionary();
295        tmp.put("fa1", new Dictionary());
296    }
297
298    void build_lipid(TreeNode node) {
299        if (tmp.containsKey("cyclo_yl")) {
300            tmp.put("fg_pos", new GenericList());
301
302            GenericList l1 = new GenericList();
303            l1.add(1);
304            l1.add("");
305            ((GenericList) tmp.get("fg_pos")).add(l1);
306
307            GenericList l2 = new GenericList();
308            l2.add((int) tmp.get("cyclo_len"));
309            l2.add("");
310            ((GenericList) tmp.get("fg_pos")).add(l2);
311
312            add_cyclo(node);
313            tmp.remove("cyclo_yl");
314            tmp.remove("cyclo_len");
315        }
316
317        if (tmp.containsKey("post_adding")) {
318            FattyAcid curr_fa_p = fattyAcylStack.peekLast();
319            int s = ((GenericList) tmp.get("post_adding")).size();
320            curr_fa_p.setNumCarbon(curr_fa_p.getNumCarbon() + s);
321            for (int i = 0; i < s; ++i) {
322                int pos = (int) ((GenericList) tmp.get("post_adding")).get(i);
323                curr_fa_p.addPosition(pos);
324                DoubleBonds db = new DoubleBonds(curr_fa_p.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds());
325                for (Entry<Integer, String> kv : curr_fa_p.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().entrySet()) {
326                    db.getDoubleBondPositions().put(kv.getKey() + (kv.getKey() >= pos ? 1 : 0), kv.getValue());
327                }
328                db.setNumDoubleBonds(db.getDoubleBondPositions().size());
329                curr_fa_p.setDoubleBonds(db);
330            }
331        }
332
333        FattyAcid curr_fa = fattyAcylStack.peekLast();
334        if (curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().size() > 0) {
335            int db_right = 0;
336            for (Entry<Integer, String> kv : curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().entrySet()) {
337                db_right += kv.getValue().length() > 0 ? 1 : 0;
338            }
339            if (db_right != curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().size()) {
340                set_lipid_level(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
341            }
342        }
343
344        Headgroup head_group = new Headgroup(headgroup);
345
346        content = new LipidAdduct();
347
348        switch (level) {
349            case COMPLETE_STRUCTURE ->
350                content.setLipid(new LipidCompleteStructure(head_group, fattyAcylStack, knownFunctionalGroups));
351            case FULL_STRUCTURE ->
352                content.setLipid(new LipidFullStructure(head_group, fattyAcylStack, knownFunctionalGroups));
353            case STRUCTURE_DEFINED ->
354                content.setLipid(new LipidStructureDefined(head_group, fattyAcylStack, knownFunctionalGroups));
355            case SN_POSITION ->
356                content.setLipid(new LipidSnPosition(head_group, fattyAcylStack, knownFunctionalGroups));
357            case MOLECULAR_SPECIES ->
358                content.setLipid(new LipidMolecularSpecies(head_group, fattyAcylStack, knownFunctionalGroups));
359            case SPECIES ->
360                content.setLipid(new LipidSpecies(head_group, fattyAcylStack, knownFunctionalGroups));
361            default -> {
362            }
363        }
364    }
365
366    void set_fatty_acyl_type(TreeNode node) {
367        String t = node.getText();
368
369        if (t.endsWith("ol")) {
370            headgroup = "FOH";
371        } else if (NOIC_SET.contains(t)) {
372            headgroup = "FA";
373        } else if (NAL_SET.contains(t)) {
374            headgroup = "FAL";
375        } else if (ACETATE_SET.contains(t)) {
376            headgroup = "WE";
377        } else if (t.equals("ne")) {
378            headgroup = "HC";
379            fattyAcylStack.peekLast().setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.ETHER);
380        } else {
381            headgroup = t;
382        }
383    }
384
385    private void add_amine(TreeNode node) {
386        FattyAcid fa = fattyAcylStack.pollLast();
387
388        fa.setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.AMIDE);
389        fattyAcylStack.getLast().setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.AMIDE);
390        fattyAcylStack.addFirst(fa);
391    }
392
393    private void set_fatty_acid(TreeNode node) {
394        FattyAcid curr_fa = fattyAcylStack.peekLast();
395        if (tmp.containsKey("length_pattern")) {
396
397            String length_pattern = (String) tmp.get("length_pattern");
398            int[] num = new int[((GenericList) tmp.get("length_tokens")).size()];
399            for (int i = 0; i < ((GenericList) tmp.get("length_tokens")).size(); ++i) {
400                num[i] = (int) ((GenericList) tmp.get("length_tokens")).get(i);
401            }
402
403            int l = 0, d = 0;
404            if (length_pattern.equals("L") || length_pattern.equals("S")) {
405                l += num[0];
406            } else if (length_pattern.equals("LS")) {
407                l += num[0] + num[1];
408            } else if (length_pattern.equals("LL") || length_pattern.equals("SL") || length_pattern.equals("SS")) {
409                l += num[0];
410                d += num[1];
411            } else if (length_pattern.equals("LSL") || length_pattern.equals("LSS")) {
412                l += num[0] + num[1];
413                d += num[2];
414            } else if (length_pattern.equals("LSLS")) {
415                l += num[0] + num[1];
416                d += num[2] + num[3];
417            } else if (length_pattern.equals("SLS")) {
418                l += num[0];
419                d += num[1] + num[2];
420            } else if (length_pattern.length() > 0 && length_pattern.charAt(0) == 'X') {
421                l += num[0];
422                for (int i = 1; i < ((GenericList) tmp.get("length_tokens")).size(); ++i) {
423                    d += num[i];
424                }
425            } else if (length_pattern.equals("LLS")) { // false
426                throw new ConstraintViolationException("Cannot determine fatty acid and double bond length in '" + node.getText() + "'");
427            }
428            curr_fa.setNumCarbon(curr_fa.getNumCarbon() + l);
429            if (curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().isEmpty() && d > 0) {
430                curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(d);
431            }
432        }
433
434        if (curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("noyloxy")) {
435            if (headgroup.equals("FA")) {
436                headgroup = "FAHFA";
437            }
438
439            while (curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("noyloxy").size() > 0) {
440                FattyAcid fa = (FattyAcid) curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("noyloxy").get(curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("noyloxy").size() - 1);
441                curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("noyloxy").remove(curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("noyloxy").size() - 1);
442
443                AcylAlkylGroup acyl = new AcylAlkylGroup(fa, knownFunctionalGroups);
444                acyl.setPosition(fa.getPosition());
445
446                if (!curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("acyl")) {
447                    curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("acyl", new ArrayList<>());
448                }
449                curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("acyl").add(acyl);
450            }
451            curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().remove("noyloxy");
452        } else if (curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("nyloxy") || curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("yloxy")) {
453            String yloxy = curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("nyloxy") ? "nyloxy" : "yloxy";
454            while (curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(yloxy).size() > 0) {
455                FattyAcid fa = (FattyAcid) curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(yloxy).get(curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(yloxy).size() - 1);
456                curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(yloxy).remove(curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(yloxy).size() - 1);
457
458                AcylAlkylGroup alkyl = new AcylAlkylGroup(fa, -1, 1, true, knownFunctionalGroups);
459                alkyl.setPosition(fa.getPosition());
460
461                if (!curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("alkyl")) {
462                    curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("alkyl", new ArrayList<>());
463                }
464                curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("alkyl").add(alkyl);
465            }
466            curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().remove(yloxy);
467        } else {
468            boolean has_yl = false;
469            for (Entry<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> kv : curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().entrySet()) {
470                if (kv.getKey().endsWith("yl")) {
471                    has_yl = true;
472                    break;
473                }
474            }
475            if (has_yl) {
476                while (true) {
477                    String yl = "";
478                    for (Entry<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> kv : curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().entrySet()) {
479                        if (kv.getKey().endsWith("yl")) {
480                            yl = kv.getKey();
481                            break;
482                        }
483                    }
484                    if (yl.length() == 0) {
485                        break;
486                    }
487
488                    while (curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(yl).size() > 0) {
489                        FattyAcid fa = (FattyAcid) curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(yl).get(curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(yl).size() - 1);
490                        curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(yl).remove(curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(yl).size() - 1);
491
492                        if (tmp.containsKey("cyclo")) {
493                            int cyclo_len = curr_fa.getNumCarbon();
494                            tmp.put("cyclo_len", cyclo_len);
495                            if (fa.getPosition() != cyclo_len && !tmp.containsKey("furan")) {
496                                switch_position(curr_fa, 2 + cyclo_len);
497                            }
498                            fa.shiftPositions(cyclo_len);
499                            if (tmp.containsKey("furan")) {
500                                curr_fa.shiftPositions(-1);
501                            }
502
503                            for (Entry<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> kv : fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().entrySet()) {
504                                if (!curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey(kv.getKey())) {
505                                    curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put(kv.getKey(), new ArrayList<>());
506                                }
507                                for (FunctionalGroup func_group : kv.getValue()) {
508                                    curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(kv.getKey()).add(func_group);
509                                }
510                            }
511
512                            curr_fa.setNumCarbon(cyclo_len + fa.getNumCarbon());
513
514                            for (Entry<Integer, String> kv : fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().entrySet()) {
515                                curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().put(kv.getKey() + cyclo_len, kv.getValue());
516                            }
517                            curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().size());
518
519                            if (!tmp.containsKey("tetrahydrofuran") && tmp.containsKey("furan")) {
520                                curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() + 2);
521                                if (!curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().containsKey(1)) {
522                                    curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().put(1, "E");
523                                }
524                                if (!curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().containsKey(3)) {
525                                    curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().put(3, "E");
526                                }
527                            }
528
529                            tmp.put("cyclo_yl", true);
530                        } else {
531                            // add carbon chains here here
532                            // special chains: i.e. ethyl, methyl
533                            String fg_name = "";
534                            if (fa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() == 0 && fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().isEmpty()) {
535                                FunctionalGroup fg = null;
536                                if (fa.getNumCarbon() == 1) {
537                                    fg_name = "Me";
538                                    fg = knownFunctionalGroups.get(fg_name);
539                                } else if (fa.getNumCarbon() == 2) {
540                                    fg_name = "Et";
541                                    fg = knownFunctionalGroups.get(fg_name);
542                                }
543                                if (fg != null && fg_name.length() > 0) {
544                                    fg.setPosition(fa.getPosition());
545                                    if (!curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey(fg_name)) {
546                                        curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put(fg_name, new ArrayList<>());
547                                    }
548                                    curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(fg_name).add(fg);
549                                }
550                            }
551                            if (fg_name.length() == 0) {
552                                CarbonChain cc = new CarbonChain(fa, fa.getPosition(), knownFunctionalGroups);
553                                if (!curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("cc")) {
554                                    curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("cc", new ArrayList<>());
555                                }
556                                curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("cc").add(cc);
557                            }
558                        }
559                    }
560                    if (tmp.containsKey("cyclo")) {
561                        tmp.remove("cyclo");
562                    }
563                    curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().remove(yl);
564                }
565            }
566        }
567
568        if (curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("cyclo")) {
569            FattyAcid fa = (FattyAcid) curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("cyclo").get(0);
570            curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().remove("cyclo");
571            if (!tmp.containsKey("cyclo_len")) {
572                tmp.put("cyclo_len", 5);
573            }
574            int start_pos = curr_fa.getNumCarbon() + 1;
575            int end_pos = curr_fa.getNumCarbon() + (int) tmp.get("cyclo_len");
576            fa.shiftPositions(start_pos - 1);
577
578            if (curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("cy")) {
579                for (FunctionalGroup cy : curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("cy")) {
580                    cy.shiftPositions(start_pos - 1);
581                }
582            }
583            for (Entry<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> kv : fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().entrySet()) {
584                if (!curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey(kv.getKey())) {
585                    curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put(kv.getKey(), new ArrayList<>());
586                }
587                for (FunctionalGroup func_group : kv.getValue()) {
588                    curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(kv.getKey()).add(func_group);
589                }
590            }
591
592            for (Entry<Integer, String> kv : fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().entrySet()) {
593                curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().put(kv.getKey() + start_pos - 1, kv.getValue());
594            }
595            curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().size());
596
597            if (!tmp.containsKey("tetrahydrofuran") && tmp.containsKey("furan")) {
598                curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() + 2);
599                if (!curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().containsKey(1 + curr_fa.getNumCarbon())) {
600                    curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().put(1 + curr_fa.getNumCarbon(), "E");
601                }
602                if (!curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().containsKey(3 + curr_fa.getNumCarbon())) {
603                    curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().put(3 + curr_fa.getNumCarbon(), "E");
604                }
605            }
606
607            curr_fa.setNumCarbon(curr_fa.getNumCarbon() + fa.getNumCarbon());
608
609            tmp.put("fg_pos", new GenericList());
610            GenericList l1 = new GenericList();
611            l1.add(start_pos);
612            l1.add("");
613            ((GenericList) tmp.get("fg_pos")).add(l1);
614            GenericList l2 = new GenericList();
615            l2.add(end_pos);
616            l2.add("");
617            ((GenericList) tmp.get("fg_pos")).add(l2);
618
619            add_cyclo(node);
620
621            if (tmp.containsKey("cyclo_len")) {
622                tmp.remove("cyclo_len");
623            }
624            if (tmp.containsKey("cyclo")) {
625                tmp.remove("cyclo");
626            }
627        } else if (tmp.containsKey("cyclo")) {
628            tmp.put("cyclo_yl", 1);
629            tmp.put("cyclo_len", curr_fa.getNumCarbon());
630            tmp.put("fg_pos", new GenericList());
631            GenericList l1 = new GenericList();
632            l1.add(1);
633            l1.add("");
634            ((GenericList) tmp.get("fg_pos")).add(l1);
635            GenericList l2 = new GenericList();
636            l2.add(curr_fa.getNumCarbon());
637            l2.add("");
638            ((GenericList) tmp.get("fg_pos")).add(l2);
639
640            tmp.remove("cyclo");
641        }
642
643        tmp.put("length_pattern", "");
644        tmp.put("length_tokens", new GenericList());
645        tmp.put("add_lengths", 0);
646    }

648    private void switch_position(FunctionalGroup func_group, int switch_num) {
649        func_group.setPosition(switch_num - func_group.getPosition());
650        for (Entry<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> kv : func_group.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().entrySet()) {
651            for (FunctionalGroup fg : kv.getValue()) {
652                switch_position(fg, switch_num);
653            }
654        }
655    }

657    private void add_cyclo(TreeNode node) {
658        int start = (int) ((GenericList) ((GenericList) tmp.get("fg_pos")).get(0)).get(0);
659        int end = (int) ((GenericList) ((GenericList) tmp.get("fg_pos")).get(1)).get(0);
660
661        DoubleBonds cyclo_db = new DoubleBonds();
662        // check double bonds
663        if (fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().size() > 0) {
664            for (Entry<Integer, String> kv : fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().entrySet()) {
665                if (start <= kv.getKey() && kv.getKey() <= end) {
666                    cyclo_db.getDoubleBondPositions().put(kv.getKey(), kv.getValue());
667                }
668            }
669            cyclo_db.setNumDoubleBonds(cyclo_db.getDoubleBondPositions().size());
670
671            for (Entry<Integer, String> kv : cyclo_db.getDoubleBondPositions().entrySet()) {
672                fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().remove(kv.getKey());
673            }
674            fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().size());
675
676        }
677        // check functionalGroups
678        HashMap<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> cyclo_fg = new HashMap<>();
679        HashSet<String> remove_list = new HashSet<>();
680        FattyAcid curr_fa = fattyAcylStack.peekLast();
681
682        if (curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("noyloxy")) {
683            ArrayList<Integer> remove_item = new ArrayList<>();
684            int i = 0;
685            for (FunctionalGroup func_group : curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("noyloxy")) {
686                if (start <= func_group.getPosition() && func_group.getPosition() <= end) {
687                    CarbonChain cc = new CarbonChain((FattyAcid) func_group, func_group.getPosition(), knownFunctionalGroups);
688
689                    if (!curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("cc")) {
690                        curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("cc", new ArrayList<>());
691                    }
692                    curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("cc").add(cc);
693                    remove_item.add(i);
694                }
695                ++i;
696            }
697            for (int ii = remove_item.size() - 1; ii >= 0; --ii) {
698                curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("noyloxy").remove((int) remove_item.get(ii));
699            }
700            if (curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("noyloxy").isEmpty()) {
701                remove_list.add("noyloxy");
702            }
703        }
704
705        for (Entry<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> kv : curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().entrySet()) {
706            ArrayList<Integer> remove_item = new ArrayList<>();
707            int i = 0;
708            for (FunctionalGroup func_group : kv.getValue()) {
709                if (start <= func_group.getPosition() && func_group.getPosition() <= end) {
710                    if (!cyclo_fg.containsKey(kv.getKey())) {
711                        cyclo_fg.put(kv.getKey(), new ArrayList<>());
712                    }
713                    cyclo_fg.get(kv.getKey()).add(func_group);
714                    remove_item.add(i);
715                }
716                ++i;
717            }
718            for (int ii = remove_item.size() - 1; ii >= 0; --ii) {
719                kv.getValue().remove((int) remove_item.get(ii));
720            }
721            if (kv.getValue().isEmpty()) {
722                remove_list.add(kv.getKey());
723            }
724        }
725        for (String fg : remove_list) {
726            curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().remove(fg);
727        }
728
729        ArrayList<Element> bridge_chain = new ArrayList<>();
730        if (tmp.containsKey("furan")) {
731            tmp.remove("furan");
732            bridge_chain.add(Element.O);
733        }
734
735        Cycle cycle = new Cycle(end - start + 1 + bridge_chain.size(), start, end, cyclo_db, cyclo_fg, bridge_chain, knownFunctionalGroups);
736        if (!fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("cy")) {
737            fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("cy", new ArrayList<>());
738        }
739        fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("cy").add(cycle);
740    }

868    private void check_db(TreeNode node) {
869        String fa_i = FA_I();
870        FattyAcid curr_fa = fattyAcylStack.peekLast();
871        if (((Dictionary) tmp.get(fa_i)).containsKey("fg_pos_summary")) {
872            for (Entry<String, Object> kv : ((Dictionary) ((Dictionary) tmp.get(fa_i)).get("fg_pos_summary")).entrySet()) {
873                int k = Integer.valueOf(kv.getKey());
874                String v = (String) ((Dictionary) ((Dictionary) tmp.get(fa_i)).get("fg_pos_summary")).get(kv.getKey());
875                if (k > 0 && !curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().containsKey(k) && (v.equals("E") || v.equals("Z") || v.length() == 0)) {
876                    curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().put(k, v);
877                    curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().size());
878                }
879            }
880        }

887    private void set_yl_ending(TreeNode node) {
888        int l = Integer.valueOf(node.getText()) - 1;
889        if (l == 0) {
890            return;
891        }
892
893        FattyAcid curr_fa = fattyAcylStack.peekLast();
894
895        if (tmp.containsKey("furan")) {
896            curr_fa.setNumCarbon(curr_fa.getNumCarbon() - l);
897            return;
898        }
899
900        String fname = "";
901        FunctionalGroup fg = null;
902        if (l == 1) {
903            fname = "Me";
904            fg = knownFunctionalGroups.get(fname);
905        } else if (l == 2) {
906            fname = "Et";
907            fg = knownFunctionalGroups.get(fname);
908        } else {
909            FattyAcid fa = new FattyAcid("FA", l, knownFunctionalGroups);
910            // shift functional groups
911            for (Entry<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> kv : curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().entrySet()) {
912                ArrayList<Integer> remove_item = new ArrayList<>();
913                int i = 0;
914                for (FunctionalGroup func_group : kv.getValue()) {
915                    if (func_group.getPosition() <= l) {
916                        remove_item.add(i);
917                        if (!fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey(kv.getKey())) {
918                            fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put(kv.getKey(), new ArrayList<>());
919                        }
920                        func_group.setPosition(l + 1 - func_group.getPosition());
921                        fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(kv.getKey()).add(func_group);
922                    }
923                }
924                for (int ii = remove_item.size() - 1; ii >= 0; --ii) {
925                    curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(kv.getKey()).remove((int) remove_item.get(ii));
926                }
927            }
928            Map<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> func_dict = curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal();
929            curr_fa.setFunctionalGroups(new HashMap<>());
930            for (Entry<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> kv : func_dict.entrySet()) {
931                if (kv.getValue().size() > 0) {
932                    curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put(kv.getKey(), kv.getValue());
933                }
934            }
935
936            // shift double bonds
937            if (curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().size() > 0) {
938                fa.setDoubleBonds(new DoubleBonds());
939                for (Entry<Integer, String> kv : curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().entrySet()) {
940                    if (kv.getKey() <= l) {
941                        fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().put(l + 1 - kv.getKey(), kv.getValue());
942                    }
943                }
944                fa.getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().size());
945                for (Entry<Integer, String> kv : fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().entrySet()) {
946                    curr_fa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().remove(kv.getKey());
947                }
948            }
949            fname = "cc";
950            fg = new CarbonChain(fa, knownFunctionalGroups);
951        }
952        curr_fa.setNumCarbon(curr_fa.getNumCarbon() - l);
953        fg.setPosition(l);
954        curr_fa.shiftPositions(-l);
955        if (!curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey(fname)) {
956            curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put(fname, new ArrayList<>());
957        }
958        curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(fname).add(fg);
959    }

999    private void add_hydroxyls(TreeNode node) {
1000        if (((GenericList) tmp.get("hydroxyl_pos")).size() > 1) {
1001            FunctionalGroup fg_oh = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
1002            ArrayList<Integer> sorted_pos = new ArrayList<>();
1003            for (Object o : (GenericList) tmp.get("hydroxyl_pos")) {
1004                int i = (int) o;
1005                sorted_pos.add(i);
1006            }
1007            Collections.sort(sorted_pos, (Integer a, Integer b) -> b.compareTo(a));
1008            for (int i = 0; i < sorted_pos.size() - 1; ++i) {
1009                int pos = sorted_pos.get(i);
1010                FunctionalGroup fg_insert = fg_oh.copy();
1011                fg_insert.setPosition(pos);
1012                if (!fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH")) {
1013                    fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("OH", new ArrayList<>());
1014                }
1015                fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(fg_insert);
1016            }
1017        }
1018    }

1035    private void add_functional_group(TreeNode node) {
1036        if (tmp.containsKey("added_func_group")) {
1037            tmp.remove("added_func_group");
1038            return;
1039        } else if (tmp.containsKey("add_methylene")) {
1040            tmp.remove("add_methylene");
1041            add_cyclo(node);
1042            return;
1043        }
1044
1045        String t = (String) tmp.get("fg_type");
1046
1047        FunctionalGroup fg = null;
1048        if (!t.equals("acetoxy")) {
1049            if (!FUNC_GROUPS.containsKey(t)) {
1050                throw new LipidException("Unknown functional group: '" + t + "'");
1051            }
1052            t = FUNC_GROUPS.get(t);
1053            if (t.length() == 0) {
1054                return;
1055            }
1056            fg = knownFunctionalGroups.get(t);
1057        } else {
1058            fg = new AcylAlkylGroup(new FattyAcid("O", 2, knownFunctionalGroups), knownFunctionalGroups);
1059        }
1060
1061        FattyAcid fa = fattyAcylStack.peekLast();
1062        if (!fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey(t)) {
1063            fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put(t, new ArrayList<>());
1064        }
1065        int l = ((GenericList) tmp.get("fg_pos")).size();
1066        for (Object o : (GenericList) tmp.get("fg_pos")) {
1067            GenericList lst = (GenericList) o;
1068            int pos = (int) lst.get(0);
1069
1070            int num_pos = 0;
1071            if (tmp.containsKey("reduction")) {
1072                for (Object oo : (GenericList) tmp.get("reduction")) {
1073                    int i = (int) oo;
1074                    num_pos += i < pos ? 1 : 0;
1075                }
1076            }
1077            FunctionalGroup fg_insert = fg.copy();
1078            fg_insert.setPosition(pos - num_pos);
1079            fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(t).add(fg_insert);
1080        }
1081    }

1085        ((Dictionary) tmp.get(FA_I())).put("db_cistrans", "");
1086    }

1088    private void add_double_bond_information(TreeNode node) {
1089        int pos = (int) ((Dictionary) tmp.get(FA_I())).get("db_position");
1090        String str_pos = Integer.toString(pos);
1091        String cistrans = (String) ((Dictionary) tmp.get(FA_I())).get("db_cistrans");
1092        if (cistrans.length() == 0 && ((Dictionary) tmp.get(FA_I())).containsKey("fg_pos_summary") && ((Dictionary) ((Dictionary) tmp.get(FA_I())).get("fg_pos_summary")).containsKey(str_pos)) {
1093            cistrans = (String) ((Dictionary) ((Dictionary) tmp.get(FA_I())).get("fg_pos_summary")).get(str_pos);
1094        }
1095        if (pos == 0) {
1096            return;
1097        }
1098
1099        cistrans = cistrans.toUpperCase();
1100
1101        ((Dictionary) tmp.get(FA_I())).remove("db_position");
1102        ((Dictionary) tmp.get(FA_I())).remove("db_cistrans");
1103
1104        if (!cistrans.equals("E") && !cistrans.equals("Z")) {
1105            cistrans = "";
1106        }
1107        if (!fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().containsKey(pos) || fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().get(pos).length() == 0) {
1108            fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().put(pos, cistrans);
1109            fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().size());
1110        }
1111    }

1117    private void set_double_bond_position(TreeNode node) {
1118        int pos = Integer.valueOf(node.getText());
1119        int num_db = 0;
1120        if (tmp.containsKey("reduction")) {
1121            GenericList gl = (GenericList) tmp.get("reduction");
1122            int l = gl.size();
1123            for (int i = 0; i < l; ++i) {
1124                num_db += ((int) gl.get(i) < pos) ? 1 : 0;
1125            }
1126        }
1127
1128        ((Dictionary) tmp.get(FA_I())).put("db_position", pos - num_db);
1129    }

1177    private void reduction(TreeNode node) {
1178        int shift_len = -((GenericList) tmp.get("fg_pos")).size();
1179        fattyAcylStack.peekLast().setNumCarbon(fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getNumCarbon() + shift_len);
1180        for (Entry<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> kv : fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().entrySet()) {
1181            for (FunctionalGroup func_group : kv.getValue()) {
1182                func_group.shiftPositions(shift_len);
1183            }
1184        }
1185
1186        tmp.put("reduction", new GenericList());
1187        for (Object o : (GenericList) tmp.get("fg_pos")) {
1188            GenericList lst = (GenericList) o;
1189            ((GenericList) tmp.get("reduction")).add((int) lst.get(0));
1190        }
1191    }

1205    private void rearrange_cycle(TreeNode node) {
1206        if (tmp.containsKey("post_adding")) {
1207            fattyAcylStack.peekLast().setNumCarbon(fattyAcylStack.peekLast().getNumCarbon() + ((GenericList) tmp.get("post_adding")).size());
1208            tmp.remove("post_adding");
1209        }
1210
1211        FattyAcid curr_fa = fattyAcylStack.peekLast();
1212        int start = (int) ((GenericList) ((GenericList) tmp.get("fg_pos")).get(0)).get(0);
1213        if (curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("cy")) {
1214            for (FunctionalGroup cy : curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("cy")) {
1215                int shift_val = start - cy.getPosition();
1216                if (shift_val == 0) {
1217                    continue;
1218                }
1219                ((Cycle) cy).rearrangeFunctionalGroups(curr_fa, shift_val);
1220            }
1221        }
1222    }

1225        tmp.put("fg_pos", new GenericList());
1226        tmp.put("fg_type", "");

1228        tmp.put(FA_I(), new Dictionary());
1229        ((Dictionary) tmp.get(FA_I())).put("recursion_pos", 0);
1230    }

1232    private void add_recursion(TreeNode node) {
1233        int pos = (int) ((Dictionary) tmp.get(FA_I())).get("recursion_pos");
1234        FattyAcid fa = fattyAcylStack.pollLast();
1235
1236        fa.setPosition(pos);
1237        FattyAcid curr_fa = fattyAcylStack.peekLast();
1238
1239        String fname = "";
1240        if (tmp.containsKey("cyclo_yl")) {
1241            fname = "cyclo";
1242            tmp.remove("cyclo_yl");
1243        } else {
1244            fname = headgroup;
1245        }
1246        if (!curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey(fname)) {
1247            curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put(fname, new ArrayList<>());
1248        }
1249        curr_fa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(fname).add(fa);
1250        tmp.put("added_func_group", 1);
1251    }
